      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个工业物联网场景下的OAuth 2.0认证流程图。核心是PLC逻辑控制器先通过MQTT Broker进行登录认证，然后获取访问令牌去请求遥测数据流。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。PLC先发起Login请求到Broker，Broker返回Access Token，然后PLC用这个Token去访问TelemetryStream对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Login",
        "Access Token",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，但这里有个细节：TelemetryStream收到Token后，会把Token和请求一起发回给PLC Logic做权限校验，不是直接放行。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Token + Request",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "那我画一个判断节点，PLC Logic检查Scope权限，通过的话走EdgeNode，拒绝的话走ActuatorController。这样分支清晰。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "Checks Scope",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以。EdgeNode是正常数据处理的绿色路径，ActuatorController是异常控制的红色路径，用不同颜色区分。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把主体流程画出来：PLC Logic → Broker → TelemetryStream → 回到PLC Logic做判断，然后分支到EdgeNode或ActuatorController。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
