      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "判断节点的标签写\"Checks Scope\"，两个分支分别标\"Yes\"和\"No\"。另外整个图要包在一个子图里，标题叫\"OAuth 2.0 Model (IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker)\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
